00:33:26.115 --> 00:33:26.470
And I saw this plan.

00:33:39.265 --> 00:33:39.590
I saw this darkness coming.

00:33:41.024 --> 00:33:42.984
And the Lord said, "You must pray.

00:34:00.560 --> 00:34:01.040
" And that's why I'm telling you, when I saw this I thought, "Is that the weapon that I saw?

