00:51:37.680 --> 00:51:40.512
So, let's see what happens.

00:51:40.512 --> 00:51:41.952
Do you remember, Braden?

00:51:41.952 --> 00:51:43.342
Yes, I remember that.

00:51:45.470 --> 00:51:45.720
I say Israel finishes the job.

